        public java.util.ArrayList<Station> planARide(GPSCoordinate beginingPoint,
                                              GPSCoordinate finishingPoint,
                                              Bike bike)
        The aim of this method is to find the shortest way to go between the location and the destination by taking at least a station, else the shortest way between two GPSCoordinate is a direct line between both.
        Specified by:
        planARide in interface PlanningRideStrategy
        Parameters:
        beginingPoint - Where the user is starting from.
        finishingPoint - Where the user wants to go.
        bike - The kind of bike the user wants (ElectricalBike, MechanicalBike)
